title: Irresistible 1-4 (of 04) (2012) (D1920) (K6DVR-Empire)
description:
English | CBR | 4 Issues

Irresistible #1-4
Publisher:  Zenescope
Publication Date:  July 25, 2012 - October 24, 2012

Writer:  Raven Gregory
Pencilers:  Derlis Santacruz (#1-2, 4) and Amin Amat (#3)
Colorists:  Franco Riesco (#1-2, 4) and Mike Stefan (#3)
Letterers:  Crank! (#1) and Jim Campbell (#2-4)

The brand new series from the mind behind the Wonderland trilogy, FLY and the Waking BEGINS HERE!!! Allen Keeg was your average middle age heart broken sap who just went through the worst break up in his life. That was a year ago. Since then Allen's been having trouble getting back into the swing of things. But all that's about to change. When Allen saves an old woman from being mugged he will be given an amazing supernatural ability that will change his whole life. But is the gift of being irresistible to every woman he meets a gift or a dreadful curse.

Thanks goes to K6DVR for this release.
